        <div id="spotify">
          <h3 class="Heading">Spotify Clone</h3>
          <p class="spotify_cont cont">This project is a web page inspired by the popular music streaming service,
            Spotify. It features a clean and user-friendly interface that allows users to browse and listen to their
            favorite music. The page includes a navigation bar, a song list with album covers, a progress bar for
            tracking the playback, and control icons for play, pause, shuffle, and repeat. The project showcases a
            visually appealing design and demonstrates skills in web development and design. It provides a familiar and
            enjoyable music streaming experience for users.
