        <div id="online_hunger">
          <h3 class="Heading">Online_hunger</h3>
          <p class="online_hunger_cont cont">This project is a simple HTML webpage for an online food delivery service
            called "Online_hunger.com." The webpage includes various sections, such as a navigation bar, a welcome
            video, information about the services offered, a section showcasing client logos, a contact form, and a
            footer. It also features responsive design elements, as indicated by the use of different CSS styles for
            different screen sizes.

            <a href="#"><video src="Video\Online_hunger_vid.mp4" alt="Online Online_hunger" class="videoSpotify"
                poster="img/Online_Hunger.png" autoplay muted loop></a>

          </p>
        </div>
        <div id="Attendence">
          <h3 class="Heading">Online Attendence System</h3>
          <p class="Attendence_cont cont">This project is an Online Attendance System designed to simplify and
            streamline the process of recording and managing attendance for educational institutions, businesses, or any
            organization that requires attendance tracking. It offers a user-friendly interface that allows users to log
            in, mark attendance, and generate reports.

            Key features of the system include user authentication for secure access, the ability to create and manage
            courses or sessions, marking attendance for students or employees, and generating detailed attendance
            reports. The project demonstrates proficiency in web development, database management, and user
            authentication, providing a valuable tool for organizations seeking to digitize and automate their
            attendance tracking processes.
